&#34;What are the rules?&#34;</p>

<p>Blinking Giles paused in his reading and looked up at Faith.
&#34;I'm not sure I understand,&#34; he said.</p>

<p>&#34;The rules,&#34; said Faith again. &#34;I wanna know what I can and
