<p>&#34;Worked?&#34; exclaimed Xander. &#34;You bet it worked!&#34;</p>

<p>With a blink Willow looked from Xander to Faith then back
again as she asked, &#34;What worked?&#34;</p>

<p>&#34;She came up with the perfect retaliation against Cordelia for
