<p>&#34;Like me,&#34; said Willow softly.</p>

<p>&#34;Yeah,&#34; Xander said as he focused his eyes on the dance floor
as Faith neared Cordelia. &#34;Like you, Will.&#34;</p>

<p>Releasing a sigh Willow followed Xander's eyes to the dance
